---
title: Sticky Miso Beef Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Veggies
description: Earthy miso, aromatic ginger and zesty lemon. This stir-fry brings together quick-cooking beef strips with a colourful array of veggies and a genius combination of Asian flavours. What's not to love?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-miso-beef-stir-fry-f8a27b1c.jpg
